but detectable\u2014bacterial sharing between species. Our study highlights the importance of using fine phylogenetic scales when assessing host specificity and suggests phylogenetic similarity may play a key role in host shifts not only for viruses but also for bacteria. Such work more broadly contributes to increasing efforts to understand cross\u2010species transmission and the epidemiological consequences of bacterial pathogens.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Becker, Daniel J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Speer, Kelly A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Brown, Alexis M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fenton, M. Brock", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Washburne, Alex D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Altizer, Sonia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Streicker, Daniel G.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Plowright, Raina K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chizhikov, Vladimir E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Simmons, Nancy B.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Volokhov, Dmitriy V.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/03145107d9200bd85804452001a44e3a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/fe75f990622ae685acbec8b572e8254b4eb68941868890b7668fc3f24ab96bd1", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/6QRM4XUQ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/6QRM4XUQ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/c5a61056e3538dc5681e4441a9c45666!/b2572-5130", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/26f7ce5dd404e33c6570edd4ba250d20", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "